<div class="title">Be Prepared and Aware</div>
<div class="substance">5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=tomstone&Exact=1">tomstone</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; tomstone. "Be Prepared and Aware: An Experience with 5-MeO-DMT (exp26302)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 22, 2003. erowid.org/exp/26302</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

